cpg.mvc.crossword

Class MainApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • cpg.mvc.crossword.MainApp

  • public class MainApp
extends javafx.application.Application
    This is the ENTRY POINT for the application. The JavaFX application extends from the Application class. Note that the start() method is abstract and must be overridden.

    First of all, this class initializes the rootLayout with the menuBar for the word editor and places it into a new scene that is placed to the primaryStage. Inside the rootLayout the wordListView is placed, this is the editor for the word data (keywords and clues).

    Primary, the rootLayout and the wordListView are shown.

    The methods generateFromSelected() and generateRendom() enable to generate a now crossword grid an present it over the crosswordPuzzleController.
